thread.title_full: Official Car Mats reviewed by Mr Garbutt

author: Mr Garbutt
title: Mr Garbutt
text: The mats for our new KIA Carens are model year specific so I was slightly worried about buying car mats from anywhere other than the dealer.I shouldn't have worried as the delivery was spot on and the quality and fit couldn't have been better.And I saved money.
